<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="id60069bdd-3a70-11f1-83b4-f01f82055b58" identifier="/us/usc/t30/s541f"><num value="541f">§ 541f.</num><heading> Disbursement of moneys</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">All moneys received under the provisions of this chapter shall be paid into the Treasury of the United States and distributed in the same manner as provided in <ref href="/us/usc/t30/s191">section 191 of this title</ref> and sections 437, 438, and 439 <ref class="footnoteRef" idref="fn002029">1</ref><note type="footnote" id="fn002029"><num>1</num> See References in Text note below.</note> of title 48.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="id60069bde-3a70-11f1-83b4-f01f82055b58">(<ref href="/us/act/1955-08-11/ch795/s7">Aug. 11, 1955, ch. 795, § 7</ref>, <ref href="/us/stat/69/681">69 Stat. 681</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
<notes type="uscNote" id="id60069bdf-3a70-11f1-83b4-f01f82055b58">
<note style="-uslm-lc:I74" role="crossHeading" topic="editorialNotes" id="id60069be0-3a70-11f1-83b4-f01f82055b58"><heading class="centered"><b>Editorial Notes</b></heading></note>
<note style="-uslm-lc:I75" topic="referencesInText" id="id60069be1-3a70-11f1-83b4-f01f82055b58">
<heading class="centered smallCaps">References in Text</heading><p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0">Sections 437, 438, and 439 of title 48, referred to in text, were repealed by <ref href="/us/pl/86/252/s1">Pub. L. 86–252, § 1</ref>, <date date="1959-09-09">Sept. 9, 1959</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/73/490">73 Stat. 490</ref>.</p>
</note>
</notes>
</section>
